data.description: This split floor plan & mint condition home is nestled in the desirable Crane Point subdivision in Sawgrass lakes. Recently this home was equipped with new stainless steel kitchen appliances. The 42-inch kitchen cabinets add beauty & sophistication to the  kitchen design. The formal living room is accentuated with a cozy fireplace. For great conversations & entertainment, the kitchen, family room, and breakfast nook are located at the heart of the house. This home also offers a separate formal living & dining room. Living areas have diagonal tile & the bedrooms offer elegant Keller Cherry laminate floors. From the screened-in patio one's eyes are instantly drawn to a panoramic view of large lake giving the property a serene ambiance. The roof is 2 years old. A must see propertyproperty
